      • asGeneric

        public IGPO asGeneric()
        Description copied from interface: IGenericSkin
        This method returns the eventual delegate that implements the IGPO interface and is primarily used to peel off a skin and gain access to implementation specific methods on the IGPO implementation object. When invoked on an object that directly implements the IGPO behavior (vs delegating the interface to an implementation object), then that object is returned. The return value is never null.

        Specified by:
        asGeneric in interface IGenericSkin
